title: 이달의소녀탐구 #362 (LOONA TV #362)
summary:
0:01 -- HeeJin is in the hallway ans is about to rehearse her performance for ViViD.
0:17 -- People at Line&Up also get to see some unreleased footage that was recorded before HeeJin's debut. She too was shocked and didn't know when she recorded it.
0:36 -- She looks at the recording and becomes nostalgic instantly. "I used to look like that~".
